                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Kätzlein Style"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cat-Claw Shield</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Cat-Claw Shield</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span></p><p>Grants 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Shield point</span> for your active character.</p><p></p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/e0be64da66db784af5d4f957d93b6fad_64541825980148024.png",
                "id": "talent27380",
                "key": "Icy Paws",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Icy Paws"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>, heals this character for 2 HP, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Drunken Mist</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/e4f93c5be05671f9b5a666361ad4812a_2504578341379306671.png",
                "id": "talent17824",
                "key": "Signature Mix",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Signature Mix"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">DMG</span>, heal your active character for 2 HP.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2504032674282208523.png",
                "id": "talent95801",
                "key": "Drunken Mist",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/998d17590e24d8a0adee347db3a6940a_8433519426754091820.png",
                "title": "Drunken Mist"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_5233779379245811813.png",
                "id": "talent86982",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8402408491807862621.png",
